  "2236590": {
    "name": "灵能觉醒",
    "steam_appid": 2236590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "在《灵能觉醒》中。白天你可以召集伙伴在野外探险、寻找龙珠、砍砍树挖挖矿，顺便挑衅一下强大的魔王。到了晚上，那些被你调戏的魔王大军在被窝儿里越想越气，势必要登高一呼，率领千军万马趁着夜色将你堵在城池里疯狂输出。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >双修少女 百万弹幕</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>目前一共有四位少女，每个人都是魔/物双修的战士，在未来还有更多的角色期待你的解锁。<br></li><li>游戏运用了当前最先进的DOTS代码，即便是老掉牙级的古董电脑，也依然能保持帧数的稳定，不明觉厉！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/caf51cc42cf0cc72094ac9cf7b4a9c4e.poster.avif?t=1744344595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/caf51cc42cf0cc72094ac9cf7b4a9c4e.webm?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/caf51cc42cf0cc72094ac9cf7b4a9c4e.mp4?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定弹幕 勇闯荒野</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>野外击杀怪物和收集资源都可以升级技能，清除巢穴还可以获得宝藏。任意组合技能都可叠加，只要你想，弹幕的形状完全可以由自己来设计。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/9809a5958d1af573a644aa73f3afac60.poster.avif?t=1744344595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/9809a5958d1af573a644aa73f3afac60.webm?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/9809a5958d1af573a644aa73f3afac60.mp4?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法多样 召唤神龙</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在盖亚母星中，玩家可以通过“酒馆”来结交好友，还可以贿赂好友与你冒险。<br></li><li>可爱的小马星球中，可以通过“马厩”，让你骑上神奇小马，在战场上一骑当千。<br></li><li>玩家可以选择【觉醒】中的【发明工坊】召唤大眼仔【工坊卫士】。<br></li><li>也可以选【许愿成真】可以集齐召唤神龙，许下您的愿望。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/e5165a172a013d991477c70fa9b654b1.poster.avif?t=1744344595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/e5165a172a013d991477c70fa9b654b1.webm?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/e5165a172a013d991477c70fa9b654b1.mp4?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >勇挑魔王 抵御大军</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>危险重重的地图上还有【魔王挑战】的功能，击败魔王，可以获得珍贵宝藏。虽然难度陡然提升，但是无双美少女又怎么会临阵退缩呢！<br></li><li>夜晚，阵地战更需要坚强的士兵和防御性建筑，游戏中的建造玩法就可以让你在面对千军万马时也能谈笑生风。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/29bace3ca48578932a8613b1925850a3.poster.avif?t=1744344595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/29bace3ca48578932a8613b1925850a3.webm?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/29bace3ca48578932a8613b1925850a3.mp4?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身骑小马 一骑当先</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>这个游戏并不孤独！游戏除了一起作战的队友还有灵能小马和驰骋沙场。哦！还有不要忘记我们的WULI KUN马哦~</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/0a633239c4f1510fcde4347a68d0b69a.poster.avif?t=1744344595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/0a633239c4f1510fcde4347a68d0b69a.webm?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236590/extras/0a633239c4f1510fcde4347a68d0b69a.mp4?t=1744344595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
